    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Transloadit OCR\nThis optional workflow uses the Transloadit OCR service to extract text from PDF documents.\nIt is particularly useful on n8n Cloud Trial or Starter plans, where available memory is more limited compared to self-hosted or Pro environments.\nIn testing, PDF files larger than ~15 MB may cause memory-related failures during extraction. Using Transloadit provides a reliable workaround by offloading processing externally.",
